children.text: Enough Said spoken word event held at Bistro 4 (4040 St. Laurent, Montreal, QC, H2W 1Y8, Canada) on March 6, 1995, hosted by Lee Gotham. Feature performances by Phineas Flower Trio and Steve Godin. Open mic/supporting performance by Ran Elfassy.
